OL,3,CBanned driver caught behind the wheel
OL,4,Cmoments after leaving court
OL,6,FA motorist who got back behind the
OL,7,Fwheel of his car to get home
OL,8,Fimmediately after leaving court with a
OL,9,Fdriving ban has been handed a
OL,10,Fsuspended jail sentence, police said.
OL,12,FRichard Brooks, 54, appeared at Newton
OL,13,FAycliffe Magistrates' Court on Monday
OL,14,F(9 February) where he was handed a six-
OL,15,Fmonth ban after being caught using his
OL,16,Fmobile phone in Barnard Castle last
OL,17,Fyear, Durham Constabulary said.
OL,19,FTraffic officers then saw him get into
OL,20,Fhis car parked at the next door Tesco
OL,21,Fstore and drive away.
