OL,3,CBanned driver caught behind the wheel
OL,4,Cmoments after leaving court
OL,6,FThe force said when he saw the
OL,7,Fofficers in their marked police
OL,8,Fvehicle, he tried to turn around and
OL,9,Fhead back into the car park.
OL,11,FOfficers arrested him, charged him
OL,12,Fwith driving while disqualified and
OL,13,Fwithout insurance and seized his car.
OL,15,FThe force said after a night in the
OL,16,Fcells Brooks was returned to the same
OL,17,Fcourt on Wednesday where his ban was
OL,18,Fincreased to 18 months and he was
OL,19,Fgiven a 12-week jail sentence,
OL,20,Fsuspended for a year.
