OL,6,FThe defendant, of Church Street,
OL,7,FGuisborough, North Yorkshire, must
OL,8,Falso complete 150 hours of community
OL,9,Fservice and pay a fine.
OL,11,FAfter the case, Sergeant Chris
OL,12,FMilburn, from Durham Roads and Armed
OL,13,FPolicing Unit, said: "This is a
OL,14,Freminder to everyone that if you're
OL,15,Fbanned from driving, then that ban
OL,16,Fstarts immediately.
